OL,3,CPolitician 'targeted by car' as
OL,4,Cofficials face growing threats
OL,6,FPoliticians from Jersey and Guernsey
OL,7,Fsay they are having to repeatedly
OL,8,Freport cases of abuse to police,
OL,9,Fincluding death threats and xenophobic
OL,10,Fattacks.
OL,12,FStates members say they fear
OL,13,Fescalating incidents of threats and
OL,14,Fharassment will put others off a
OL,15,Fcareer in politics and can endanger
OL,16,Fthem.
