OL,3,CPolitician 'targeted by car' as
OL,4,Cofficials face growing threats
OL,6,F"The danger is that this intimidates
OL,7,Fthe good people from standing. Why
OL,8,Fwould they stand? They may want to
OL,9,Fgive back to their community, but they
OL,10,Fdon't want to necessarily receive the
OL,11,Fabuse from a minority."
OL,13,FDeputy Meerveld says he is far from
OL,14,Falone in receiving abuse and added:
OL,15,F"Some have been sent threatening notes
OL,16,Fsaying, 'I know where you live and
OL,17,Fwhere your kids go to school.'"
