OL,3,CPolitician 'targeted by car' as
OL,4,Cofficials face growing threats
OL,6,FThe island's former Chief Minister,
OL,7,FDeputy Peter Ferbrache, has been
OL,8,Ftargeted with hateful slander online -
OL,9,Fanother Guernsey politician was
OL,10,Fassaulted in a pub, and one even found
OL,11,Fhuman faeces on their doorstep.
OL,13,FIn Jersey, one politician said they
OL,14,Fhad beer poured over their head.
