OL,3,CPolitician 'targeted by car' as
OL,4,Cofficials face growing threats
OL,6,FAnother, Deputy Kirsten Morel,
OL,7,Fexplained: "What I've seen over the
OL,8,Fpast year or so, particularly around
OL,9,Fthe ferry decision, is that people on
OL,10,Fsocial media can make it incredibly
OL,11,Fpersonal and be aggressive with what
OL,12,Fthey say.
OL,14,F"That's really difficult for anybody
OL,15,Fto deal with, when it's dozens of
OL,16,Fpeople. But it's also really hard on
OL,17,Fthe families - I know my family find
OL,18,Fit really hard.
