OL,3,CPolitician 'targeted by car' as
OL,4,Cofficials face growing threats
OL,6,F"My big fear is that people don't want
OL,7,Fto end up running for election ... all
OL,8,Fit does is erode democracy."
OL,10,FDeputy Inna Gardiner has shared some
OL,11,Fof the abuse she faced online with ITV
OL,12,FNews, which she reported to the police.
OL,14,FThe comments are deeply offensive and
OL,15,Fxenophobic.
